{
  "texts": [
    "U-Net segmentation maps will help further in the quantification of size and shape of a lesion for further treatment planning and disease monitoring.",
    "Automation within the framework thus reduces variability and enhances consistency in diagnosis; it also has some potential applications in telemedicine, which would extend remote analysis of colonoscopy data.",
    "These applications position PolynetDWTCADx well for its role in improving diagnostic efficiency, clinical workload, and patient outcomes.",
    "The outputs of the PolyNetDWTCADx framework are highly interpretable segmentation maps and classification predictions that can be directly used in clinical workflows.",
    "Segmentation maps obtained via the U-Net component give very much accurate delineation of cancerous regions; these let clinicians understand very well the size, the shape, and the extension of the lesions."
  ]
}